org.apache.james.mailbox.copier

Interface MailboxCopier

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MailboxCopierImpl

    public interface MailboxCopier
    Interface that exposes a method aimed to copy all mailboxes from a source mailbox manager to a destination mailbox manager.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void copyMailboxes(MailboxManager src, MailboxManager dest)
      Copy the mailboxes from a mailbox manager to another mailbox manager.

    • Method Detail

      • copyMailboxes

        void copyMailboxes(MailboxManager src,
                 MailboxManager dest)
                   throws MailboxException,
                          IOException
        Copy the mailboxes from a mailbox manager to another mailbox manager. The implementation is responsible to read all mailboxes form the injected srcMailboxManager and to copy all its contents to the dstMailboxManager.

        dest -
        Throws:
